{"tid":2518307,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蔡玉玲拍《鏗鏘集》圓夢　任職港台幸福10年","createTime":"2021-05-06T02:40:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-06T05:39:25.000Z","uid":130626,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3988fb98720471e2f5ec1e4aa4bba1f629c828e4","tid":2518307,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T02:40:12.000Z","msg":"《鏗鏘集》曾是不少記者的「終極目標」，蔡玉玲也一樣。高中時看到《鏗》訪問社工王惠芬協助少數族裔，她深受感動，「原來可以咁樣去報道人哋嘅事」，立志要拍攝紀錄片。2005年中大新聞系畢業後，蔡先到無綫電視擔任綜藝節目編導，兩年後獲港台公共事務組聘用為非公務員合約員工。<br />\n<br />\n進入公共事務組後，由《議事論事》做起，2012年正式加入《鏗》，「圓咗自己一個小小嘅夢想」。蔡2014年成為公務員，2016年因想做更多調查報道而轉往《傳真社》，奈何《傳真社》經營困難，她2018年底以CAT II身份重返港台。<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210506/7VF5BJ37NJGZVDVCV57TSEFJ5E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210506%2F7VF5BJ37NJGZVDVCV57TSEFJ5E%2F&d=lnSleIYCVJUMUgC9CFuHQsE4f%2F6cKlXs%2FdqEvpC7bjY%3D&h=0319ac8e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210506%2F7VF5BJ37NJGZVDVCV57TSEFJ5E%2F&h=7c9a3607\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210506/7VF5BJ37NJGZVDVCV57TSEFJ5E/</a>"},{"pid":"66ee251149f74875e96e3cef18f688b6aef13275","tid":2518307,"uid":260121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T02:43:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e0acf987e4132a8270264eadf41fac2c5f51dc5","tid":2518307,"uid":288675,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T02:44:56.000Z","msg":"以前唯一不以政治考慮既電視台<br />\n現在係唯一以政治考慮既電視台<br />\n文匯大公可以不理"},{"pid":"a1983fb5624810e9f080c871d86a224b83958fa1","tid":2518307,"uid":204539,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T02:47:57.000Z","msg":"真心想做好記者職責嘅記者<br />\nrespect<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ca5961b39ff7c4b4c0e67bae605275b3f7c8af7","tid":2518307,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1983f